;; adr.edn — machine-readable ADR registry for the kotoba workspace.
;;
;; Single source of truth for "which architecture decisions exist, their status,
;; and how they relate." Kept in EDN (the project's canonical data notation —
;; same reader as kotoba-edn) so tooling can query it. Each :file is relative to
;; docs/. Add a new entry whenever a docs/ADR-*.md lands; keep :status in sync
;; with the document's own Status line.
{:schema  1
 :updated "2026-07-02"

 :adrs
 [{:id         :adr-tensor-artifacts-ipld-raw-leaves
   :file       "ADR-tensor-artifacts-ipld-raw-leaves.md"
   :title      "Tensor artifacts as IPLD raw leaves — CID/IPLD を維持した CPU/LLM 分散推論のデータ面"
   :status     :proposed
   :date       "2026-07-02"
   :topics     #{:inference :llm :gguf :tensor :ipld :cid :dag-cbor :raw-leaf :bitswap :tensor-parallel :kv-cache :arrow :zstd :num-clj :dedup :mmap}
   :note       "Control plane は DAG-CBOR/CIDv1 を維持し、テンソル実体だけを quant-block 整列の IPLD raw leaf (0x55) + dag-cbor manifest に分解する。モデル同一性は :kotodama/digest (SHA-256 hex) から manifest CID へ。shard 配布は kotoba.net.bitswap の want-list に還元。KV-cache/activation などホットパスは content-address せず libp2p QUIC 上の raw frame。Arrow IPC は columnar バッチ I/O 限定で frame=raw leaf として IPLD と両立。圧縮はトランスポート層のみ・CID は非圧縮 byte に対して計算。"}

