  {:id         :adr-002-stake-to-replicate
   :file       "ADR-002-stake-to-replicate.md"
   :title      "Stake-to-replicate: a bonded, reputation-weighted replica membrane"
   :status     :accepted-phased
   :date       "2026-06-17"
   :extends    :adr-001-five-axis
   :realises   "GROWTH-DECENTRALIZATION.edn p6"
   :crate      "crates/kotoba-dht"
   :topics     #{:distributed :availability :sybil :economics :mishmar :replication}
   :note       "Wires existing primitives (NeighborhoodBlockStore / AvailabilityChallenge→verify_proof / SettlementBatch / Mishmar observation / witness quorum) into a replica membrane gated by an observed on-chain bond, with non-transferable reputation as preference only. Respects the Mishmar read+verify-only boundary (no on-chain signing/custody/settlement in kotoba). Separates collateral (slashable) from reputation (non-transferable, decaying)."}

